§M{m001:Pipeline}
  §F{f001:FetchAndStore:pub} (str:url) -> i32
    §B{~closed} false
    §TR{t1}
      §B{data} §C{FetchRemote} §A url §/C
      §B{rc} §C{WriteRecord} §A data §/C
      §R rc
    §CA{NetworkError:ne}
      §R -1
    §CA{IoError:ie}
